From: Jeffy Chen <jeffy.chen@rock-chips.com>
Date: Mon, 5 Dec 2022 16:48:12 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 79/97] gl-renderer: Fix crash when painting views without
 buffer

By adding a sanity check for gb.

Signed-off-by: Jeffy Chen <jeffy.chen@rock-chips.com>
---
 libweston/renderer-gl/gl-renderer.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/libweston/renderer-gl/gl-renderer.c b/libweston/renderer-gl/gl-renderer.c
index 55f03d1..95241af 100644
--- a/libweston/renderer-gl/gl-renderer.c
+++ b/libweston/renderer-gl/gl-renderer.c
@@ -1345,6 +1345,9 @@ draw_paint_node(struct weston_paint_node *pnode,
 	GLint filter;
 	struct gl_shader_config sconf;
 
+	if (!gb)
+		return;
+
 	if (gb->shader_variant == SHADER_VARIANT_NONE &&
 	    !buffer->direct_display)
 		return;
